entries.npc_11: Forget it.  I'll get a Wookiee to do it next time.  At least they don't talk back.
entries.npc_10: I think you've done a pretty good job of confusing yourself.
entries.npc_5: Oh dear...you do know what a machine is right?
entries.npc_9: Then don't play dumb.  Where are my parts?
entries.npc_8: Which part of the sentence confused you then?  Did.  You.  Bring.  My.  Parts?  Forget it....(sigh)
entries.npc_3: You do know what parts are right?  Machine parts?  Metal and gears?  Make stuff work?
entries.npc_7: Forget it.  You're not the delivery guy.  Sorry.  Thought you were someone else.
entries.npc_6: Great.  What use are you to me then?
entries.npc_2: The parts I ordered!  Did you bring them or not?
entries.player_2: I don't know what you mean?
entries.npc_1: I'm the technician here.  Did you bring my parts?
